842  an improvement on donnell approximation for thinwalled circular cylinders   morley,lsd  q j mech app math 12, 1959  an improvement on donnell approximation for thinwalled circular cylinders    donnell equation for thinwalled circular cylinders is replaced by where w is a nondimensional form of the radial displacement and q is the distributed radial loading   this equation retains the essential simplicity of the original but, unlike donnell equation, the accuracy does not decrease as the wavelength of circumferential distortion increases  
